// Scenario catalog for bug-simulator. Empty in v0.1.0.
//
// Each entry is keyed by scenario id and declares:
//   niche_type: rotting_log | phytotelma | carrion | leaf_litter | dung |
//               tree_hole | soil_profile
//   locality: human-readable real place
//   initial_substrate: substrate profile at t=0 (per-zone defaults the
//                       NicheGeometry builder will distribute over cells)
//   initial_resources: ResourceProfile fields at t=0 for the whole niche
//   colonization_pool: { species_id: per_day_rate } for stochastic arrivals
//   events: [ { step, kind, params } ] — scheduled perturbations
//   expected_species: catalog assertions for end-state assemblage
//
// First scenario to author (per PROPOSAL-BUG-SIMULATOR.md): a beech log
// at year 5 post-fall in Białowieża primeval forest, with four
// species — Trametes versicolor (sessile fungus), Glomeris marginata
// (millipede), Ceratophysella denticulata (springtail), Lithobius
// forficatus (centipede).

{}
